msgid "The maximized area fill the whole application window. You can maximize an area with :menuselection:`View --> Toggle Maximize Area` menu entry or keyboard shortcut :kbd:`Ctrl-Spacebar`. To return to normal size use keyboard shortcut or the *Back to Previous* button on the Top bar."
